articles.title: World's oldest boomerang older than thought, but not Australian - BBC
articles.description: The 40,000-year-old boomerang was made with an astonishing level of skill and ingenuity, say scientists.
articles.content:
Helen Briggs
The boomerang was found near stones, animal and human bones
